# terraform-provider-{{ shortName }}

A [Terraform](https://www.terraform.io/) provider for {{ shortName }}, built with [terrably](https://github.com/paambaati/terrably).

## Using the provider

```hcl
terraform {
  required_providers {
    {{ shortName }} = {
      source  = "<your-namespace>/{{ shortName }}"
      version = "~> 0.1"
    }
  }
}

provider "{{ shortName }}" {
  # Configuration options
}
```
